        The personal data we collect includes:
        <ul class="list-bullet">
            <li>names</li>
            <li>addresses</li>
            <li>contact details</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <p>
        We are allowed to process your data because we have official authority as the
        environmental regulators for the WEEE regulations. The lawful basis for processing your
        personal data is to perform a task in the public interest that is set out in law.
    </p>

    <p>
        If you do not give us the information requested, you may be in breach of your conditions of
        approval which could lead to your approval being withdrawn and / or prosecution.
